<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>환자 프로필 페이지</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css"> <!-- 스타일시트 링크 -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Pretendard-Regular', sans-serif;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .main-container {
            display: flex;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .profile-container {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 300px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            height: fit-content;
            position: sticky;
            top: 20px; /* Adjust based on header height */
        }
        .content-container {
            flex: 3;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .profile-card {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .profile-image {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background: url('https://i.imgur.com/3beQH5s.jpeg') no-repeat center center;
            background-size: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        .profile-details {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .chart-container, .diary-entries, .message-book {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="profile-container">
            <%- include('./profile_components/profile_card') %>
        </div>
        <div class="content-container">
            <div class="chart-container">
                <h2>나의 감정 차트</h2>
                <img src="https://i.imgur.com/Q6rwO2A.png" alt="감정 차트" style="width:100%;">
            </div>
            <div class="diary-entries">
                <h2>일기 목록</h2>
                <div class="entry">
                    <h3>오늘의 일기 1</h3>
                    <p>오늘은 마음이 많이 편안한 날이었습니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="entry">
                    <h3>오늘의 일기 2</h3>
                    <p>오늘은 행복한 일이 많았습니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="message-book">
                <h2>상담사 방명록</h2>
                <div class="message">
                    <p>구체적인 상담내용 세부사항 기재</p>
                </div>
                <div class="message">
                    <p>구체적인 상담내용 세부사항 기재</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
